{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG image element","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">« Previous</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">Next  »</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The SVG <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/image\"><code>&lt;image&gt;</code></a> element allows for raster images to be rendered within an SVG object.</p>\n<p>In this basic example, a .jpg image referenced by an <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/href\">href</a></code> attribute will be rendered inside an SVG object:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token prolog\">&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" standalone=\"no\"?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">svg</span> <span class=\"token name\">PUBLIC</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"-//W3C//DTD SVG 1.1//EN\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token string\">\"http://www.w3.org/Graphics/SVG/1.1/DTD/svg11.dtd\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>svg</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>4cm<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">version</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n     <span class=\"token attr-name\">xmlns</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/2000/svg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\"><span class=\"token namespace\">xmlns:</span>xlink</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>image</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>firefox.jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>svg</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>There are some important things to take note of (referenced from the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG/struct.html#ImageElement\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3 specs</a>):</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>If you do not set the <code>x</code> or <code>y</code> attributes, they will be set to <code>0</code>.</li>\n  <li>If you do not set the <code>height</code> or <code>width</code> attributes, they will be set to <code>0</code>.</li>\n  <li>Having a <code>height</code> or <code>width</code> attribute of <code>0</code> will disable rendering of the image.</li>\n</ul><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">« Previous</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Tools_for_SVG\">Next  »</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"The SVG <image> element allows for raster images to be rendered within an SVG object.","popularity":0.0008,"modified":"2022-09-09T05:38:45.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVG: Elément image","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG の image 要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SVG 이미지 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"SVG image element","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/svg/tutorial/svg_image_tag","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/svg/tutorial/svg_image_tag/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/f22e42182591e38590c9add80de91a51bce3cde2","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial","title":"SVG Tutorial"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_Image_Tag","title":"SVG image element"}],"pageTitle":"SVG image element - SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics | MDN","noIndexing":false}}